io.klerch.alexa.tellask.schema

Interface AlexaLaunchHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AlexaRequestHandler

    public interface AlexaLaunchHandler
extends AlexaRequestHandler
    An interface for a AlexaLaunchHandler handling a launch event in your skill. It doesn't make sense to have more than one of these handlers in your skill project. It's necessary to have one at all. The handler will only be considered to handle a launch request by tagging the implementation class with the AlexaLaunchListener-annotation.

      • Methods inherited from interface io.klerch.alexa.tellask.schema.AlexaRequestHandler
